ship over here?

459
00:21:44,291 --> 00:21:47,291
Why would they go to
all that trouble for us?

460
00:21:52,708 --> 00:21:54,708
Ranmaru.

461
00:21:54,791 --> 00:21:56,250
[gasps]

462
00:22:02,875 --> 00:22:06,000
That mask! It can't be!

463
00:22:06,083 --> 00:22:08,791
But, who... is that?

464
00:23:48,791 --> 00:23:52,208
[CHIBI cries] A scary ship
appeared out of nowhere!

465
00:23:52,291 --> 00:23:53,791
